ClassDesc: Object that encapsulates a request to @B_com#google#android#gms#identity#intents#Address#requestUserAddress_E@. If your app only allows addresses in certain countries, then you can use this object to specify these countries and the API will only return an address if it is an applicable country. If you do not specify any countries, then it will be assumed that there are no restrictions.
